  <figure class="container-prose post-hero">
    <img src="/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/ChatGPT-Image-Nov-11-2025-12_03_58-AM.png" alt="Landlord Responsibilities: What You're Really Signing Up For (And What You're Not)" width="1200" height="675" loading="eager" />
